Question
========

In a study with two factors, A (3 level factors) and B (2 level factors), the following is found:

  -------- ---- ----- ---- --- Source df SS MS F A 2 120 60 B 1 80 80 A 2 Error 25 225 9 Total 30 500 -------- ---- ----- ---- ---

The null hypothesis of no interaction can be accepted at significance level 0.05

Answerlist
----------

* Be rejected.
* Not be rejected.
* Not be determined.

Solution
========

Answerlist
----------

* Be rejected..: Correct
* Not be rejected...: Incorrect
* Not be determined...: Incorrect
